4
00:09:24,981 --> 00:09:27,245
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}弗兰克先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Frank.

5
00:09:27,317 --> 00:09:29,308
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}弗兰克先生？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Frank?

6
00:09:34,457 --> 00:09:36,448
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}卡勒？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Kraler?

7
00:09:40,263 --> 00:09:42,697
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}卡勒先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Kraler.

8
00:09:42,765 --> 00:09:44,756
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}米耶普
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Miep.

9
00:09:47,603 --> 00:09:49,537
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我的好朋友
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}My good friends.

10
00:09:49,605 --> 00:09:51,539
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}噢，很......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Oh, it...

11
00:09:51,607 --> 00:09:54,872
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}很高兴见到你回家
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}it is so good to see you home.

12
00:09:54,944 --> 00:09:56,935
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们没得到任何消息
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We had heard nothing.

13
00:09:59,949 --> 00:10:02,213
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我就一个人
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm alone.

14
00:10:02,285 --> 00:10:05,220
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你得和我们一起回家
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You must come home with us...

15
00:10:05,288 --> 00:10:07,256
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}现在去休息
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}and rest now.

16
00:10:07,323 --> 00:10:11,817
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-你必须和我们呆在一起，   -不，米耶普，我不能留在阿姆斯特丹
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- You must stay with us. - No, Miep. I can't stay in Amsterdam.

17
00:10:13,096 --> 00:10:16,930
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}弗兰克先生，这里是你的家
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Frank, this is your home.

18
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,934
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}阿姆斯特丹是你的家
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Amsterdam is your home.

19
00:10:19,002 --> 00:10:21,436
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}这里让我回忆起太多了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It has too many memories for me.

20
00:10:21,504 --> 00:10:23,438
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}到处触景伤情，到处
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Everywhere there's something, Miep. Everywhere.

21
00:10:23,506 --> 00:10:26,236
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}甚至见到你和卡勒先生的时候
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Even seeing you and Mr. Kraler.

22
00:10:29,312 --> 00:10:32,748
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}原谅我，你们做了那么多，我不该这样和你们说话
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Forgive me. I shouldn't talk to you like this after all that you did.

23
00:10:32,815 --> 00:10:34,806
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们还会那么做的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We would do it again.

24
00:10:36,819 --> 00:10:39,686
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}什么都没有了--那本书
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Everything's gone-- the book.

25
00:10:39,756 --> 00:10:41,690
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他们拿走了一切
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}They took everything...

26
00:10:41,758 --> 00:10:43,692
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}除了一些文件
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}except some papers.

27
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:46,251
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们保存了你的信件和文件
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We saved your letters and papers.

28
00:10:52,341 --> 00:10:54,741
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}请把那些烧掉
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Please burn them.

29
00:10:54,810 --> 00:10:56,744
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}烧掉所有东西
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Burn everything.

30
00:10:56,812 --> 00:10:59,747
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我...... 我......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I... I...

31
00:10:59,815 --> 00:11:03,945
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}告诉安妮，如果我回来，我会找到她的书
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}told Anne if I got back here, I'd find her book.

32
00:11:04,020 --> 00:11:07,786
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}安妮日记？那就是她留下那本书的地方
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Anne's diary? It's where she left it.

33
00:11:58,474 --> 00:12:02,467
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"1942年7月9日"
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"The ninth of July, 1942."

34
00:12:04,313 --> 00:12:07,146
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}1942年，有可能吗，米耶普？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}1942. Is it possible, Miep?

35
00:12:07,216 --> 00:12:10,014
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}才3年前
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Only three years ago.

36
00:12:10,086 --> 00:12:14,022
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"亲爱的日记，自从你我要成为最好的朋友......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"Dear Diary, since you and I are going to be great friends...

37
00:12:14,090 --> 00:12:17,526
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我就要告诉你我所有的一切了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"I will start by telling you all about myself.

38
00:12:17,593 --> 00:12:19,788
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我叫安妮・弗兰克
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"My name is Anne Frank.

39
00:12:19,862 --> 00:12:21,796
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}13岁
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"I am 1 3 years old.

40
00:12:21,864 --> 00:12:23,798
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我生在德国
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"I was born in Germany...

41
00:12:23,866 --> 00:12:25,800
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}但是因为我家是犹太人......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"but since my family is Jewish...

42
00:12:25,868 --> 00:12:29,304
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}在希特勒上台后，我们移民到了荷兰
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"we emigrated to Holland when Hitler came to power.

43
00:12:29,372 --> 00:12:32,307
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们的一切都开始好转
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Things went well for us...

44
00:12:32,375 --> 00:12:35,310
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}直到战争降临，德国占领了这里
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"until the war came,and the German occupation.

45
00:12:35,378 --> 00:12:38,313
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}犹太人的处境变得很差
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"Then things got very bad for the Jews.

46
00:12:38,381 --> 00:12:41,908
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不可以做这个，不可以做那个
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You could not do this, and you could not do that.

47
00:12:41,984 --> 00:12:44,919
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们必须佩戴黄色星星标志
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We had to wear yellow stars.

48
00:12:44,987 --> 00:12:47,251
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我必须上缴我的自行车
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I had to turn in my bike.

49
00:12:47,323 --> 00:12:50,258
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我再也不能去荷兰人的学校
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I couldn't go to a Dutch school anymore.

50
00:12:50,326 --> 00:12:53,762
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不能看电影，不能坐小汽车......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I couldn't go to the movies or ride in an automobile...

51
00:12:53,829 --> 00:12:55,763
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}甚至不能坐公车
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}or even on a streetcar...

52
00:12:55,831 --> 00:12:58,595
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}还有无数其他的事情
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}and a million other things.

53
00:12:58,667 --> 00:13:03,263
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}但是不管怎样，我们小孩还是尽力快活起来
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}but somehow we children still managed to have fun.

54
00:13:03,339 --> 00:13:06,604
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}今天早晨爸爸5点就叫醒我......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}This morning father woke me at 5:00...

55
00:13:06,675 --> 00:13:10,111
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他告诉我快点起来穿衣服
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}and told me to hurry and get dressed.

56
00:13:10,179 --> 00:13:12,773
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们要去躲起来
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We were going into hiding.

57
00:13:12,848 --> 00:13:16,113
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我要穿上尽可能多的衣服
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I was to put on as many clothes as I could.

58
00:13:16,185 --> 00:13:20,178
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}如果我们带着箱子出去，会引起怀疑
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It would look too suspicious if we walked along carrying suitcases.

59
00:13:21,657 --> 00:13:24,217
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们要消失......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We were going to disappear...

60
00:13:24,293 --> 00:13:26,955
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}在空气中蒸发
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}vanish into thin air.

61
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:34,192
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我活在冒险中
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm living a great adventure.

62
00:13:41,710 --> 00:13:44,144
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}还有3个人和我们一起
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Three other people were coming in with us.

63
00:13:44,213 --> 00:13:47,011
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}爸爸认识他们，但是我从来没有见过他们
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}father knew them, but we had never met them.

64
00:13:58,994 --> 00:14:00,894
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}一定发生什么事了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Something's happened.

65
00:14:00,963 --> 00:14:02,897
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他们得徒步走3英里
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}They have three miles to walk.

66
00:14:02,965 --> 00:14:05,399
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-妈妈......  -我知道他们被抓了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Mother...   - They've been arrested. I know.

67
00:14:05,468 --> 00:14:08,028
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-你们能停下吗？   -妈妈！爸爸！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Will you stop that? - Mother! father!

68
00:14:08,103 --> 00:14:10,401
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们在这儿
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We're here.

69
00:14:10,473 --> 00:14:12,464
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}都到了吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}See?

70
00:14:15,010 --> 00:14:16,944
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-范・戴恩先生  -你好，你好
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Mr. Van Daan. - Hello, hello.

71
00:14:17,012 --> 00:14:20,106
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-范・戴恩太太。彼得。  -弗兰克先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Mrs. Van Daan. Peter. - Mr. Frank.

72
00:14:20,182 --> 00:14:23,117
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}大街上到处都是环保警察
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}There were too many of the Green Police on the streets.

73
00:14:23,185 --> 00:14:25,619
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们必须绕远
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We had to take the long way around.

74
00:14:25,688 --> 00:14:29,988
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}介绍自己了吗？这是我女儿安妮，我妻子埃蒂茨
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Did you introduce yourself? My daughter Anne. My wife Edith.

75
00:14:30,059 --> 00:14:31,993
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-玛戈特。范・戴恩先生太太。  -你好
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Margot. Mr. and Mrs. Van Daan. - Hello.

76
00:14:32,061 --> 00:14:34,996
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-噢，这是我们的儿子彼得
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Oh, and this is our son Peter.

77
00:14:35,064 --> 00:14:39,933
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}那么，请，让我们脱下一部分衣服
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}So, now, please, let us take off some of these clothes.

78
00:14:40,002 --> 00:14:41,936
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}早上好
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Good morning.

79
00:14:42,004 --> 00:14:44,438
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-早上好，卡勒先生。  --早上好，卡勒先生。
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Hello, Mr. Kraler. - Good morning, Mr. Kraler.

80
00:14:44,507 --> 00:14:47,101
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}弗兰克先生。啊，你们都在这儿，不错。
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Frank. Ah, you're all here. That is good.

81
00:14:47,176 --> 00:14:49,610
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们本来希望做的有条不紊
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We had hoped to have everything in order.

82
00:14:49,678 --> 00:14:52,112
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}卡勒先生，请不要那么想
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Please, Mr. Kraler, don't even think of it.

83
00:14:52,181 --> 00:14:55,116
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}要知道，我们有足够空闲时间安排我们的一切
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}After all, we'll have plenty of leisure to arrange everything ourselves.

84
00:14:55,184 --> 00:14:58,119
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-我带了些三明治做你们的午餐。   -谢谢，米耶普
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- I brought sandwiches for your lunch. - Thank you, Miep.

85
00:14:58,187 --> 00:15:01,122
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}灌装食物在这儿，还有你们要储存的干豆和马铃薯
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}The canned goods are here, and your stores of dried beans and potatoes.

86
00:15:01,190 --> 00:15:04,626
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-我下午把定量供给证拿来。   -定量供给证？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- I'll get ration books this afternoon. - Ration books?

87
00:15:04,693 --> 00:15:07,958
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}如果他们看到供给证上有我们的名字，就会知道我们在这里了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}If they see our names on ration books, they'll know we're here.

88
00:15:08,030 --> 00:15:11,193
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}别担心，上边不会写你们的名字
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Don't worry. It won't be your names that'll be on them.

89
00:15:14,670 --> 00:15:16,604
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}爸爸！西部教堂！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}father! The Westertoren!

90
00:15:16,672 --> 00:15:18,663
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}安妮，不！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Anne, no!

91
00:15:19,775 --> 00:15:22,209
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}永远不要碰那扇窗帘，永远不要.
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You must never touch a curtain. Never.

92
00:15:22,278 --> 00:15:25,714
