450
00:42:40,493 --> 00:42:43,428
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-哦，闭嘴。  -你把所有的钱全抽光了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Oh, stop it. - You're smoking up all our money!

451
00:42:43,496 --> 00:42:45,862
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}能闭嘴吗！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Will you shut up!

452
00:42:49,435 --> 00:42:51,426
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你在盯着什么？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And what are you staring at?

453
00:42:52,705 --> 00:42:55,538
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我过去从来没有见过大人这样吵架
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I never heard grown-ups quarrel like that before.

454
00:42:55,608 --> 00:42:57,542
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我还以为只有小孩才打架
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I thought only children quarreled.

455
00:42:57,610 --> 00:43:00,579
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}这不是吵架，是讨论
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}This isn't a quarrel. It's a discussion.

456
00:43:00,647 --> 00:43:03,912
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-我都没见过孩子这么粗鲁。  -我，粗鲁？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- And I never heard children so rude. - I, rude?

457
00:43:03,983 --> 00:43:05,917
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-是的。  -安妮，喝你的牛奶！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Yes! - Anne, drink your milk.

458
00:43:05,985 --> 00:43:09,887
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你的麻烦是，你被惯坏了。你需要的是打屁股
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}The trouble with you is, you've been spoiled. You need a spanking.

459
00:43:09,956 --> 00:43:12,891
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}记住，某某先生，我是一个淑女
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Remember, Mr. So-and-so, that I am a lady.

460
00:43:12,959 --> 00:43:15,894
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你太让人恼火......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mmm, you're the most aggravating...

461
00:43:15,962 --> 00:43:18,897
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}为什么你不能像你的妹妹玛戈特那样优雅，安静一些？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Why aren't you nice and quiet like your sister Margot?

462
00:43:18,965 --> 00:43:21,399
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}为什么你非得一直卖弄自己？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Why do you have to show off all the time?

463
00:43:21,467 --> 00:43:24,903
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}让我给你一点忠告，年轻人――男人可不喜欢那样的女孩
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Let me give you a little advice, young lady-- men don't like that in a girl.

464
00:43:24,971 --> 00:43:28,407
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你喜欢吗？一个男人喜欢听话的女孩
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Do you know that? A man likes a girl who will listen to him once in a while.

465
00:43:28,474 --> 00:43:32,410
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-喜欢知道做饭，打扫的女孩。  -我宁可抹脖子
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- A girl who loves to cook and clean-- - I'd cut my throat first!

466
00:43:32,478 --> 00:43:34,742
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我要张扬个性
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'd open my veins.

467
00:43:34,814 --> 00:43:37,146
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我要与众不同
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm going to be remarkable.

468
00:43:37,216 --> 00:43:39,081
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我要去巴黎......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm going to Paris...

469
00:43:39,152 --> 00:43:41,279
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-巴黎？是的，是的。  -去学音乐和美术
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Paris? Yeah, yeah. - to study music and art.

470
00:43:41,354 --> 00:43:45,518
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我要做演员，作家或者舞蹈家
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm going to be an actress, or a writer, or a dancer.

471
00:43:47,727 --> 00:43:49,661
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-看你做的事情。  -对不起
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Look what you did. - I'm so sorry.

472
00:43:49,729 --> 00:43:52,163
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你这个笨蛋！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You clumsy little fool!

473
00:43:52,231 --> 00:43:55,166
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-这是我爸爸留给我的大衣！  -对不起
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- This is the coat my father gave me! - I'm so sorry.

474
00:43:55,234 --> 00:43:58,169
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你把大衣毁了。怎么这么不小心？你毁了大衣！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You ruined it. What do you care? Ruined it!

475
00:43:58,237 --> 00:44:01,172
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我要杀了你！我真想杀了你！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I could kill you! I could just kill you!

476
00:44:01,240 --> 00:44:04,676
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}佩特罗内拉。宝贝，宝贝
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Petronella. Liebchen, Liebchen.

477
00:44:04,744 --> 00:44:06,678
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}佩特罗内拉
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Petronella.

478
00:44:06,746 --> 00:44:08,680
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}只是件大衣而已
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It's only a coat.

479
00:44:08,748 --> 00:44:11,683
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}安妮，你不可以那个样子
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Anne, you must not behave in that way.

480
00:44:11,751 --> 00:44:14,982
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}只是一个意外，谁都会出意外
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It was an accident. Anyone can have an accident.

481
00:44:15,054 --> 00:44:17,989
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我不是那意思，我是说你顶嘴
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I don't mean that. I mean the answering back.

482
00:44:18,057 --> 00:44:19,991
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你不可以顶嘴
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You must not answer back.

483
00:44:20,059 --> 00:44:21,993
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他们都是客人
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}They're our guests.

484
00:44:22,061 --> 00:44:25,326
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}玛戈特从来没有那样和客人争吵，不是吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You don't hear Margot getting into any arguments with them, do you?

485
00:44:25,398 --> 00:44:27,832
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}向玛戈特学学
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Try to be like Margot.

486
00:44:27,900 --> 00:44:31,836
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}让他们象踩玛戈特那样踩我吗？不，谢谢了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And have them walk all over me the way they do her? No, thanks.

487
00:44:31,904 --> 00:44:34,839
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我不知道你到底怎么了，安妮
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I don't know what happens to you, Anne.

488
00:44:34,907 --> 00:44:38,035
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}要是当初我也象你对我说话那样，对我妈妈说话......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}If I had ever talked to my mother as you talk to me--

489
00:44:38,111 --> 00:44:39,976
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}一切都在变，妈妈
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Things have changed, Mother.

490
00:44:40,046 --> 00:44:42,310
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}大家都不那样了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}People aren't like that anymore.

491
00:44:42,382 --> 00:44:46,318
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}“是，妈妈。”，“不，妈妈”，“听你的，妈妈。”
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"Yes, Mother." "No, Mother." "Anything you say, Mother."

492
00:44:46,386 --> 00:44:48,854
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我必须为自己努力争取
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I've got to fight things out for myself.

493
00:44:48,921 --> 00:44:50,855
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-但是......    -争取自己应得的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- But...   - Make something of myself.

494
00:44:50,923 --> 00:44:53,858
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}没必要去吵吵嚷嚷去争啊。玛戈特就不吵嚷
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It isn't necessary to fight to do it. Margot doesn't fight.

495
00:44:53,926 --> 00:44:55,860
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}玛戈特！我耳朵都灌满了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Margot! That's all I hear.

496
00:44:55,928 --> 00:44:57,862
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}“为什么你不象玛戈特？”
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"Why aren't you like Margot?"

497
00:44:57,930 --> 00:45:01,366
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}她做什么都是对的，我做什么都是错的！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Everything she does is right, and everything I do is wrong!

498
00:45:01,434 --> 00:45:05,268
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你们都看不上我，你最看不上我！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You're all against me, and you worst of all!

499
00:45:09,075 --> 00:45:12,010
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我不知道这样过日子，还能挺多久
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I don't know how we can go on living this way.

500
00:45:12,078 --> 00:45:15,343
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我一句都不能说安妮了，她和我吵来吵去
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I can't say a word to Anne, she flies at me.

501
00:45:15,415 --> 00:45:19,351
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你了解安妮。不出半小时她就会连说带笑地出来
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You know Anne. In a half hour she'll be out here laughing and joking.

502
00:45:19,419 --> 00:45:21,683
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}并且，呃...
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And, uh...

503
00:45:21,754 --> 00:45:24,689
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我告诉你爸爸这样根本不行――两家在一起
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I told your father it wouldn't work-- two families.

504
00:45:24,757 --> 00:45:27,692
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不，不，他会问的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}But no, no, he had to ask them.

505
00:45:29,762 --> 00:45:31,753
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}嘘
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Shh.

506
00:45:49,315 --> 00:45:52,250
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}每次听到声音，我的心跳都要停了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Every time I hear that sound, my heart stops.

507
00:45:52,318 --> 00:45:54,309
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-是米耶普。  -爸爸！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- It's Miep. - father!

508
00:45:55,721 --> 00:45:57,712
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-啊？  -是米耶普
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Yes? - It's Miep.

509
00:46:01,527 --> 00:46:03,961
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}这是你开的单子
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Here's your list.

510
00:46:04,030 --> 00:46:05,964
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-是米耶普吗？  -是的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Is it Miep? - Yes.

511
00:46:06,032 --> 00:46:07,966
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我终于能等到一些烟卷了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}At last I'll have some cigarettes.

512
00:46:08,034 --> 00:46:09,968
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}米耶普来了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Miep's here.

513
00:46:10,036 --> 00:46:13,472
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我都不好意思说我对那件大衣有多抱歉
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I can't tell you how sorry I am about the coat.

514
00:46:13,539 --> 00:46:15,473
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}没事了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Don't worry.

515
00:46:15,541 --> 00:46:17,475
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-你好，你好。  -米耶普
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Hello, hello. - Miep.

516
00:46:17,543 --> 00:46:19,477
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}卡勒先生！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Kraler!

517
00:46:19,545 --> 00:46:22,480
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}卡勒先生一露面，就阳光灿烂
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}When Mr. Kraler comes, the sun begins to shine.

518
00:46:22,548 --> 00:46:25,483
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-德克不得不离开了。  -德克是米耶普的未婚夫？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Dirk has had to leave. - Dirk is Miep's fianc?

519
00:46:25,551 --> 00:46:28,987
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他得躲到乡下去，摆脱那些工人的电话
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He had to go into hiding in the country to escape a labor call-up.

520
00:46:29,055 --> 00:46:31,990
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}但是他让我给你们带来一台收音机
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}But he has let me have the radio for you.

521
00:46:32,058 --> 00:46:33,992
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他不该这样
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He shouldn't have.

522
00:46:34,060 --> 00:46:35,994
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}哦，太危险了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Oh, it was too dangerous.

523
00:46:36,062 --> 00:46:37,996
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}看！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Look!

524
00:47:37,890 --> 00:47:39,824
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们珍贵的收音机
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Our blessed radio.

525
00:47:39,892 --> 00:47:44,056
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}给了我们了解外面世界的眼睛和耳朵
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It gives us our eyes and ears out into the world.

526
00:47:44,130 --> 00:47:47,065
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们只听德国电台的好听音乐
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We listen to the German station only for good music.

527
00:47:47,133 --> 00:47:50,068
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}轴心国军队在西部沙漠......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}The Axis forces in the Western desert...

528
00:47:50,136 --> 00:47:52,570
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}为了希望，我们听着BBC
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And we listen to the BBC for hope.

529
00:47:52,638 --> 00:47:55,573
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}对我们陆空力量的持续攻击......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Ceaseless attacks by our land and air forces...

530
00:47:55,641 --> 00:47:57,575
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}现在已经完全被遏制了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}are now in full retreat.

531
00:47:57,643 --> 00:48:01,079
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}英国军队在持续推进
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}The Eighth Army continues to advance.

532
00:48:01,147 --> 00:48:04,207
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}好消息
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}That's good.

533
00:48:04,283 --> 00:48:08,276
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}好吧，彼得。让我们听听他们会说纳粹什么
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}All right, Peter, now let's see what they have to say about the Nazis.

534
00:48:12,358 --> 00:48:14,292
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}柏林
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Berlin.

535
00:48:48,694 --> 00:48:51,162
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}还要听吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Must we listen?

536
00:48:53,332 --> 00:48:55,630
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}行了，彼得，够了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}All right, Peter. That's enough.

537
00:49:36,762 --> 00:49:39,595
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}环保警察，他们发现我们了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}The Green Police. They've found us.

538
00:50:28,848 --> 00:50:30,839
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}嗯
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Hmm.

539
00:50:44,997 --> 00:50:46,988
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}嗯
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Hmm.

540
00:50:50,035 --> 00:50:52,026
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}啊
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Ah.

541
00:51:26,438 --> 00:51:28,429
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}嘘
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Huh.

542
00:51:47,192 --> 00:51:49,183
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}嘘
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Huh.

543
00:51:52,031 --> 00:51:54,022
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}嘘
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Hmm.

544
00:54:15,574 --> 00:54:17,565
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}这边走，达索尔先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}This way, Mr. Dussel.

545
00:55:12,865 --> 00:55:16,460
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-是卡勒，请开门。   -还有米耶普
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- It is Kraler. Please open. - And Miep.

546
00:55:16,535 --> 00:55:18,560
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}噢，保佑他们，他们来了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Oh, bless them. They are here.

547
00:55:18,637 --> 00:55:22,903
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-卡勒？  -还有米耶普。请开门
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-Kraler? -And Miep,yes. Open, please.

548
00:55:27,146 --> 00:55:31,776
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-哦，昨晚来了一个访客。  -昨晚一个访客？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Well, we had a visitor last night. - A visitor last night?

549
00:55:31,850 --> 00:55:33,511
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-是的，是的。  -一个窃贼
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Yes, yes. - A thief.

550
00:55:33,585 --> 00:55:35,416
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-那是个窃贼？  -你听到了？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- It was a thief? - Did you hear him?

551
00:55:35,487 --> 00:55:37,318
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-是的，我们听到了。  -他就在你们下面
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Yes, we heard him. - He was right under you.

552
00:55:37,389 --> 00:55:40,222
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-正下面的办公室里。  -我们不知道
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- In the office right under here. - We did not know.

553
00:55:40,292 --> 00:55:42,692
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们还以为是环保警察
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We thought it was the Green Police.

554
00:55:42,761 --> 00:55:47,562
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-你能肯定吗，米耶普？  -当然，你们那时安静吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Are you sure, Miep? - You were, of course, quiet?

555
00:55:47,633 --> 00:55:51,626
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们没有动，甚至整晚都几乎没有呼吸
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We didn't move. We hardly breathed all night.

556
00:55:51,703 --> 00:55:55,696
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-很好，很近啊。  -太近了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- That is good. It was close. - Too close.

557
00:55:55,774 --> 00:55:58,140
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他把桌子和所有的档案翻了个底朝天
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He went through everything. The desk and the files.

558
00:55:58,210 --> 00:56:01,805
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}桌子和所有的档案，并且也发现保险柜了，但是没能打开
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}The desk and the files. And he found the safe, but he could not get it open.

559
00:56:01,880 --> 00:56:04,542
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他在找我们从黑市弄的口粮供应卡
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He was looking for our ration card supply from the Underground.

560
00:56:04,616 --> 00:56:06,948
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-有人知道。  -都在那个保险柜里
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Somebody knows. - They're in that safe.

561
00:56:07,019 --> 00:56:11,956
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他们还会回来。扔掉保险柜吧，从这儿弄出去。
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}They'll come back. Get rid of that safe. Get it out of here.

562
00:56:12,024 --> 00:56:14,083
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}是的。门上贴个条子：
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Yes. Put a sign on the door:

563
00:56:14,159 --> 00:56:16,684
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}“窃贼，别回来了，保险柜已经没有了。”
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"Burglars, do not come back. The safe is gone."

564
00:56:16,762 --> 00:56:17,990
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}笑话而已
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Jokes, yet.

565
00:56:18,063 --> 00:56:20,327
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-弗兰克先生，我得和你谈谈。  -好的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Mr. Frank, I must talk to you. - Yes, of course.

566
00:56:20,399 --> 00:56:22,594
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}或许是那台收音机。我们应该丢掉它
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Maybe it's the radio. We should get rid of the radio.

567
00:56:22,668 --> 00:56:26,126
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}扔到炉子里烧了吧。要是环保警察发现收音机......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Put it in the stove, burn it. If the Green Police found that radio...

568
00:56:26,205 --> 00:56:28,196
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}或许还会发现她的日记。我们也要烧掉
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And they'd find her diary. We'll burn that too.

569
00:56:28,273 --> 00:56:30,138
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我的日记不可以
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Not my diary.

570
00:56:30,209 --> 00:56:33,144
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-我和日记共存亡。   -日记在哪？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- My diary goes, I go with it. - Where is it?

571
00:56:33,212 --> 00:56:36,340
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}要是他们发现我们，他们同样会发现日记和收音机
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}If they find us, they might just as well find the diary, the radio.

572
00:56:36,415 --> 00:56:37,916
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}有什么不同吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}What'll be the difference?

573
00:56:38,417 --> 00:56:41,648
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-我来的时候，总是尽力带好消息。  -是的，我知道
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- When I come, I try to bring good news. - Yes, I know.

574
00:56:41,720 --> 00:56:44,211
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}发生了一件事，一个男人来找我
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Something has happened. A man came to me.

575
00:56:44,289 --> 00:56:47,224
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他告诉我他有一个犹太朋友，一个牙医
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He told me that he has a Jewish friend-- a dentist.

576
00:56:47,292 --> 00:56:51,228
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他求我帮他找个藏身地方，所以我来找你
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He begged me, could I find him a hiding place? So I have come to you.

577
00:56:51,296 --> 00:56:54,629
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我知道很难说出口，象你们这样的状况......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I know it is a terrible thing to ask, living the way you are...

578
00:56:54,700 --> 00:56:57,692
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}把他带来了吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}but could you take him in?

579
00:56:57,769 --> 00:57:00,966
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-嗯，当然我们会收留。  -他叫让・达索尔
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Well, of course we will. - His name is Jan Dussel.

580
00:57:01,039 --> 00:57:05,476
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-达索尔，等等，我认识他。  -留下他很不错
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Dussel. Wait. I think I know him. - It's fine to have him.

581
00:57:05,544 --> 00:57:08,308
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}但是，奥托，我们把他放在哪儿啊？哪里？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}But, Otto, where are we going to put him? Where?

582
00:57:08,380 --> 00:57:10,729
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}吃的这么少，还收留另外一个人......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}There's so little food as it is, and to take in another person...

583
00:57:10,862 --> 00:57:12,727
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们一人省一口就可以，范・戴恩先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We can stretch the food a little, Mr. Van Daan.

584
00:57:12,797 --> 00:57:15,357
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-他可以用我的床。  -不用，谢谢你，彼得
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- He can have my bed. - No, thank you, Peter.

585
00:57:15,433 --> 00:57:17,924
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}玛戈特搬到我们这儿，他可以用她的床
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Margot will move in here with us, and he can have her bed.

586
00:57:18,003 --> 00:57:21,336
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我把东西拿出来
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'll get my things out.

587
00:58:00,512 --> 00:58:02,446
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}达索尔先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Dussel.

588
00:58:11,690 --> 00:58:14,352
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}别碰到头
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Don't bump your head.

589
00:58:17,629 --> 00:58:21,292
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}进来，达索尔先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Come in, Mr. Dussel.

590
00:58:21,366 --> 00:58:25,029
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-这位是弗兰克先生。   -奥托・弗兰克先生？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- This is Mr. Frank. - Mr. Otto Frank?

591
00:58:25,103 --> 00:58:27,799
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}是。把东西给我
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Yes. Let me have your things, please.

592
00:58:27,872 --> 00:58:31,467
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}谢谢，弗兰克先生。我把你交给他们了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Thank you, Mr. Frank. I leave you in good hands.

593
00:58:31,543 --> 00:58:33,272
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-达索尔先生？  -嗯？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Mr. Dussel? - Hmm?

594
00:58:33,345 --> 00:58:36,007
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我得把大衣拿回去
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I must return your coat.

595
00:58:37,916 --> 00:58:40,214
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我该怎么谢你啊？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}What can I say to thank you?

596
00:58:40,285 --> 00:58:44,187
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}卡勒先生，米耶普。他们是我们的生命线。没有他们，我们都活不了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Kraler, Miep, they're our lifeline. Without them, we couldn't live.

597
00:58:44,255 --> 00:58:47,088
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}哦，你说的好像我们很崇高，并不是那样
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Please,you make us seem very heroic. It isn't that at all.

598
00:58:47,158 --> 00:58:51,060
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们只是不喜欢纳粹，不喜欢他们的所作所为......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We simply don't like the Nazis. We don't like their methods...

599
00:58:51,129 --> 00:58:54,792
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我知道。“没人告诉我们荷兰人该怎样对待该死的犹太人。”
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I know. "Nobody's gonna tell us Dutchmen what to do with our damn Jews."

600
00:58:54,866 --> 00:58:58,962
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们明早上来看看，他们会对你很好的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We will be up tomorrow to see that they are treating you right.

601
00:58:59,037 --> 00:59:01,301
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-再见。  -再见，卡勒先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Good-bye. - Good-bye, Mr. Kraler.

602
00:59:01,373 --> 00:59:02,931
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}再见，米耶普
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Good-bye, Miep.

603
00:59:03,008 --> 00:59:06,171
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}欢迎，达索尔先生。   -谢谢
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Welcome, Mr. Dussel. - Thank you.

604
00:59:06,244 --> 00:59:09,873
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}这是我妻子，埃蒂茨。范・戴恩先生太太
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}This is my wife, Edith. Mr. and Mrs. Van Daan.

605
00:59:09,948 --> 00:59:14,442
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他们的儿子，彼得。我的女儿玛戈特和安妮
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Their son, Peter, my daughters Margot and Anne.

606
00:59:14,519 --> 00:59:16,919
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-安妮。   -你好
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Anne. - How do you do.

607
00:59:16,988 --> 00:59:21,755
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}玛戈特。   -达索尔先生，请坐
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Margot. - Please, Mr. Dussel, sit down.

608
00:59:22,761 --> 00:59:25,457
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}谢谢
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Thank you.

609
00:59:25,530 --> 00:59:28,226
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我知道我在做梦
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm dreaming, I know it.

610
00:59:28,299 --> 00:59:31,598
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}奥托・弗兰克先生，这儿
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Otto Frank, here.

611
00:59:31,670 --> 00:59:36,232
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}那么你们不在瑞士？有人说你们逃到瑞士去了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You're not in Switzerland, then? Someone said that you escaped to Switzerland.

612
00:59:38,209 --> 00:59:41,872
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-你们一直在这儿？  -从七月份就一直在
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- And you've been here all this time? - Ever since July.

613
00:59:44,215 --> 00:59:48,208
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}卡勒先生没告诉你这里吃的东西不多吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Did Mr. Kraler warn you you won't get much to eat here?

614
00:59:48,286 --> 00:59:53,451
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你可以想象......我们七个人就三张配给卡
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You can imagine... three ration cards among the seven of us.

615
00:59:53,525 --> 00:59:56,858
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}现在是八个人了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Now you make eight.

616
00:59:56,928 --> 01:00:00,420
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}范・戴尔先生，你还不知道外面在发生什么......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Van Daan, you don't realize what's happening outside...

617
01:00:00,498 --> 01:00:03,160
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你不该那样警告我
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}that you should warn me of a thing like that.

618
01:00:04,636 --> 01:00:09,300
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你还不知道在这里，阿姆斯特丹，在发生什么
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You don't realize what's going on right here in Amsterdam.

619
01:00:09,374 --> 01:00:11,569
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}每天成百上千的犹太人失踪
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Every day, hundreds ofJews disappear.

620
01:00:13,978 --> 01:00:18,574
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他们包围街区，一户一户搜查
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}They surround a block, and they search house by house.

621
01:00:20,351 --> 01:00:25,015
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}每天都有孩子们放学回到家，发现父母消失了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Every day children come home from school to find their parents gone.

622
01:00:26,357 --> 01:00:28,348
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}成百成千的人被驱逐出境了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Hundreds are being deported.

623
01:00:30,929 --> 01:00:34,626
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你我都认识的人――豪恩斯坦一家，维塞尔一家。
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}People that you and I know--the Hallensteins, the Wessels.

624
01:00:34,699 --> 01:00:36,633
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}噢，不
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Oh, no.

625
01:00:36,701 --> 01:00:39,727
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你会收到通知书
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You get your call-up notice

626
01:00:39,804 --> 01:00:43,797
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}通知你某天某时到火车站
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}come to the station on such and such a day and hour.

627
01:00:43,875 --> 01:00:46,537
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}只能带着随身的东西
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Bring only what you can carry.

628
01:00:46,611 --> 01:00:50,047
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}要是你不离开，他们就来把你拖走
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}If you don't go, they come and drag you from your home...

629
01:00:50,115 --> 01:00:53,050
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}用船运到茅斯奥森――死亡营
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}and ship you off to Mauthausen-- the death camp.

630
01:00:53,118 --> 01:00:55,552
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们不知道情况会变得这么糟
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We didn't know that things had got so much worse.

631
01:00:55,620 --> 01:00:59,112
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}原谅我说那些
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Forgive me for speaking so.

632
01:00:59,190 --> 01:01:02,387
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你认识德・沃瑞斯一家嘛？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Do you know the de Vries?

633
01:01:02,460 --> 01:01:04,451
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他们走了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}They're gone.

634
01:01:10,335 --> 01:01:13,702
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}珊妮和我同班
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Sanne and I are in the same class.

635
01:01:13,772 --> 01:01:17,572
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}珊妮是我最好的――最好的朋友
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Sanne is my best-- my best friend.

636
01:01:17,642 --> 01:01:21,806
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}她放学回家发现父母不见了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}She returned home from school to find her parents gone.

637
01:01:24,082 --> 01:01:28,416
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}她自己呆了两天，来人就把她带走了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}She was alone for two days, and then they came and took her away.

638
01:01:31,089 --> 01:01:33,080
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}走了？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Gone?

639
01:01:39,764 --> 01:01:42,096
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}和所有其他人
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}With all the others.

640
01:01:43,701 --> 01:01:46,192
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}噢，不
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Oh, no.

641
01:01:52,377 --> 01:01:55,369
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}还有叫梅耶伯格的，就住在我们附近......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Some people named Meyerberg, they lived near us...

642
01:01:55,446 --> 01:01:58,006
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我想我们晚些时候在谈这些吧，范・戴恩太太
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I think we should put this off until later, Mrs. Van Daan.

643
01:01:58,082 --> 01:02:00,243
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我肯定达索尔先生需要安顿一下了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm sure Mr. Dussel would like to get settled now.

644
01:02:00,318 --> 01:02:03,310
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}安妮，把达索尔先生带到他的房间好吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Annele, would you like to take Mr. Dussel to his room?

645
01:02:03,388 --> 01:02:06,050
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}请跟我来，达索尔先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}If you'll come with me, Mr. Dussel.

646
01:02:08,660 --> 01:02:13,324
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}哦，不胜感激
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Uh, forgive me if I haven't expressed my gratitude.

647
01:02:14,599 --> 01:02:18,592
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}这是对我多大的打击啊
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}This has been such a shock to me.

648
01:02:18,670 --> 01:02:21,605
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我一直认为自己是荷兰人
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I always thought of myself as Dutch.

649
01:02:21,673 --> 01:02:24,267
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我生在荷兰
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I was born in Holland.

650
01:02:24,342 --> 01:02:28,369
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我爸爸生在荷兰，我爷爷也生在荷兰
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}My father was born in Holland, and my grandfather.

651
01:02:28,446 --> 01:02:32,780
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}过了这么多年......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And now after all these years...

652
01:02:35,286 --> 01:02:37,777
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}失陪了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}If you will excuse me.

653
01:03:16,427 --> 01:03:19,919
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}和卡勒先生告诉我们的太不一样了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It's so different from what Mr. Kraler tells us.

654
01:03:19,998 --> 01:03:22,626
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}卡勒先生说情况在改善
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Kraler says that things are improving.

655
01:03:22,700 --> 01:03:26,636
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我宁愿是卡勒先生说的那样
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I like it better the way Kraler tells it.

656
01:04:19,023 --> 01:04:21,014
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}晚上好，巴比勒
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Good night, Bubele.

657
01:04:22,827 --> 01:04:26,319
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-该说晚安了。   -晚安，妈妈
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Say good night. - Good night, Mother.

658
01:04:31,502 --> 01:04:33,231
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-晚安，弗兰克先生。   -晚安
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Good night, Mr. Frank. - Good night.

659
01:04:33,304 --> 01:04:35,795
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}晚安
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Good night.

660
01:04:37,975 --> 01:04:40,967
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你有孩子吗，达索尔先生？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Do you have any children, Mr. Dussel?

661
01:04:41,045 --> 01:04:44,037
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}没有，我没结婚
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}No, I never married.

662
01:04:47,818 --> 01:04:51,151
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-你没有亲人吗？  - 一个也没有
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Have you no family at all? - No one.

663
01:04:55,693 --> 01:05:00,995
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}太可怕了，你一定相当孤独
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}How dreadful. You must be terribly lonely.

664
01:05:01,065 --> 01:05:04,728
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}嗯，我已经习惯了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mm. I'm used to it.

665
01:05:04,802 --> 01:05:08,465
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我肯定不会习惯
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I don't think I could get used to it.

666
01:05:10,341 --> 01:05:13,572
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-你有宠物吗？一只猫或者一条狗？  -没有
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Didn't you have a pet? A cat or a dog? - No.

667
01:05:13,644 --> 01:05:18,638
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不，不。我对带毛动物过敏
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}No, no. I have an allergy to fur-bearing animals.

668
01:05:18,716 --> 01:05:22,652
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-会让我哮喘。  -哦，天啊
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Gives me asthma. - Oh, dear.

669
01:05:22,720 --> 01:05:25,553
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-怎么了？   -彼得有只猫
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- What? - Peter has a cat.

670
01:05:25,623 --> 01:05:30,390
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-他有？他有只猫在这儿？  -是的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- He has? He has it here? - Yes.

671
01:05:51,248 --> 01:05:55,184
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们很少见到，彼得一直在自己房间养它
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We hardly ever see it. He keeps it in his room all the time.

672
01:05:55,252 --> 01:05:57,584
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我相信会好的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm sure it will be all right.

673
01:05:57,655 --> 01:05:59,646
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}啊哈，那么，希望如此吧
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mm-hmm. Well, I hope so.

674
01:06:04,929 --> 01:06:07,989
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我希望不会太打扰你，达索尔先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I hope I'm not going to be too much of a bother to you, Mr. Dussel.

675
01:06:08,065 --> 01:06:09,999
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不会的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}No.

676
01:06:10,067 --> 01:06:13,559
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我好像能让每个人都生气
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I seem to be able to get everyone's back up.

677
01:06:13,637 --> 01:06:17,630
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}哦，我总是和孩子们相处很好
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Oh, I always get along very well with young people.

678
01:06:17,708 --> 01:06:20,302
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我的病人都把他们的孩子带来......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}My patients all bring their children to me...

679
01:06:20,377 --> 01:06:23,471
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}因为他们知道我和孩子们合得来
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}because they know I get along well with them.

680
01:06:23,547 --> 01:06:25,538
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}所以不必担心
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}So don't you worry about that.

681
01:06:27,017 --> 01:06:29,815
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}谢谢，达索尔先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Thank you, Mr. Dussel.

682
01:06:29,887 --> 01:06:33,721
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}晚安，我马上回来
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Good night. I'll be back.

683
01:06:33,791 --> 01:06:37,454
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}晚安，达索尔先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Good night, Mr. Dussel.

684
01:06:43,634 --> 01:06:45,727
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}当心
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Careful.

685
01:08:36,380 --> 01:08:38,905
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}珊妮
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Sanne.

686
01:08:38,983 --> 01:08:41,474
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}珊妮？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Sanne?

687
01:08:41,552 --> 01:08:43,713
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}珊妮
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Sanne.

688
01:08:55,099 --> 01:08:58,000
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}停！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Halt!

689
01:09:12,116 --> 01:09:14,880
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}救救我！救救我！不，不！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Save me! Save me! No, no!

690
01:09:14,952 --> 01:09:18,718
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-不！不，不要碰我！  -住手。住手
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Oh! No, don't take me! - Stop it. Stop it.

691
01:09:27,531 --> 01:09:30,830
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-救救我。   -安静，亲爱的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-Save me. -Hush, darling.

692
01:09:30,901 --> 01:09:33,369
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}安静。没事了。没事了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Hush. It's all right. It's all right.

693
01:09:33,437 --> 01:09:36,964
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}达索尔先生，请打开灯。只是个梦
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Please, Mr. Dussel, turn on the light. It was just a dream.

694
01:09:37,041 --> 01:09:39,942
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你在这里，很安全。知道吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You're here, safe. You see?

695
01:09:40,010 --> 01:09:44,003
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}这孩子一定有什么事，那么大声叫
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Something must be done with that child, yelling like that.

696
01:09:44,081 --> 01:09:48,142
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}谁知道什么人会在街上。她危及到我们生命了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Who knows who might be in the street. She's endangering all our lives.

697
01:09:48,218 --> 01:09:52,712
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}达索尔先生，毕竟安妮不是训练有素的前线士兵
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Dussel, after all, Anne is not exactly a trained, frontline soldier.

698
01:09:52,790 --> 01:09:55,725
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}达索尔先生，请回去睡觉吧
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Please, Mr. Dussel, go back to bed.

699
01:09:55,793 --> 01:09:59,194
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}过一两分钟她就会好，对吗，安妮？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}She'll be herself in a minute or two. Won't you, Anne?

700
01:10:01,331 --> 01:10:04,494
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}回去睡觉
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Go back to bed.

701
01:10:06,236 --> 01:10:11,674
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}打扰下，我要去厕所，唯一安静的地方
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Excuse me. I'm going to the W.C., the one room where there's peace.

702
01:10:11,742 --> 01:10:14,074
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}现在回去睡觉
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Go back to bed now.

703
01:10:14,144 --> 01:10:18,808
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}要点水吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Would you like some water?

704
01:10:18,882 --> 01:10:22,477
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}是个恶梦吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Was it a very bad dream?

705
01:10:22,553 --> 01:10:24,680
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}也许你能告诉我
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Perhaps if you told me.

706
01:10:24,755 --> 01:10:28,953
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-我宁可不说。  -好好睡觉吧
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- I'd rather not talk about it. - Try to sleep then.

707
01:10:30,794 --> 01:10:34,958
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-我就坐在你旁边。  -不用的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- I'll sit right here beside you. - You don't have to.

708
01:10:36,233 --> 01:10:40,693
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我真的非常想陪你
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}But I'd like to stay with you very much. Really.

709
01:10:40,771 --> 01:10:43,205
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}真的不用了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'd rather you didn't.

710
01:10:48,579 --> 01:10:52,743
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}晚安...
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Good night...

711
01:10:57,421 --> 01:11:01,790
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}没事吧？什么也不要吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You'll be all right? There's nothing that you want?

712
01:11:01,859 --> 01:11:06,023
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}能让爸爸过来吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Will you please ask father to come?

713
01:11:11,702 --> 01:11:14,694
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}当然，安妮宝贝
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Yes, of course, Anne dear.

714
01:11:22,412 --> 01:11:25,404
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}她叫你
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}She asks for you.

715
01:11:26,450 --> 01:11:29,351
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-埃蒂茨。   -去吧，奥托
