01:12:02,849 --> 01:12:05,682
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}只是一个年龄阶段而已
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It's just a phase.

722
01:12:05,752 --> 01:12:08,687
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}所有的女孩在这个阶段都要爸爸
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}All girls turn to their fathers at this age.

723
01:12:08,755 --> 01:12:11,121
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}把所有的爱给爸爸
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}They give all their love to their fathers.

724
01:12:11,191 --> 01:12:15,321
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你不该这样，不该排斥我
