725
01:12:17,597 --> 01:12:19,531
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}那么......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}So...

726
01:12:21,201 --> 01:12:23,533
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}那么，要不要我给你读一会书？
