729
01:12:30,377 --> 01:12:35,280
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不。现在安静地躺着。就这样
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}No. Now lie down quietly. So, like this.

730
01:12:35,348 --> 01:12:37,942
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}现在使劲睡着吧
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Now try to sleep.

731
01:12:38,018 --> 01:12:43,684
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我是个胆小鬼。我对自己失望极了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm a terrible coward. I'm so disappointed in myself.

732
01:12:46,159 --> 01:12:48,525
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我想我真的已经长大了......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I think I'm really grown up...

733
01:12:48,595 --> 01:12:52,395
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}然后发生事情，我却象小孩一样跑到你身边
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}and then something happens and I run to you like a baby.

734
01:12:52,465 --> 01:12:55,298
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我爱你，爸爸。除了你，我谁也不爱
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I love you, father. I don't love anyone but you.

735
01:12:55,368 --> 01:12:57,734
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}安妮。安妮。
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Annele. Annele.

736
01:12:57,804 --> 01:13:01,467
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}真的，你是我唯一爱的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It's true. You're the only one I love.

737
01:13:01,541 --> 01:13:05,534
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我已经想很长时间了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I've been thinking about it for a long time.

738
01:13:05,612 --> 01:13:10,345
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}很好，能告诉我你爱我 ，那很好......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It's fine-- It's fine to have you tell me that you love me...

739
01:13:10,417 --> 01:13:14,649
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}但是，要是你能告诉我你也爱你妈妈，我会更高兴
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}but I'd be much happier if you said that you loved your mother as well.

740
01:13:14,721 --> 01:13:17,884
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}她太需要你的帮助了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}She needs your help so much.

741
01:13:19,159 --> 01:13:22,060
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-那时你的爱。  -我们没有共同语言
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Your love. - We have nothing in common.

742
01:13:22,128 --> 01:13:24,562
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}她不理解我
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}She doesn't understand me.

743
01:13:24,631 --> 01:13:28,362
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}每当我想说说对生命的看法，她就问我是不是便秘
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Whenever I try to explain my views on life, she asks me if I'm constipated.

744
01:13:30,203 --> 01:13:34,367
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}刚才你太伤她心了。她在哭。在那里哭呢
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You hurt her very much just now. She's crying. She's in there crying.

745
01:13:43,283 --> 01:13:48,482
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}噢，爸爸，我是不是很可怕？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Oh, father, I was horrible, wasn't I?

746
01:13:48,555 --> 01:13:51,547
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我怎么了？告诉我
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}What's the matter with me? Tell me.

747
01:13:51,625 --> 01:13:54,594
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不要说这是要经历的阶段。帮帮我
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Don't say it's just a phase. Help me.

748
01:13:57,030 --> 01:14:01,865
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}安妮，父母对孩子能做的太少啊
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}There's so little we parents can do to help our children, Anne.

749
01:14:01,935 --> 01:14:06,429
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们只是尽力作个好榜样，指出一条路
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We can only try to set a good example. Point the way.

750
01:14:06,506 --> 01:14:09,066
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}其余的都得靠你自己
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}The rest you must do yourself.

751
01:14:09,142 --> 01:14:13,704
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我在努力，真的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm trying. Really, I am.

752
01:14:13,780 --> 01:14:18,945
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}每天晚上我都在反省我过去做过的所有错事
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Every night I think back over all the things I did that day that were wrong.

753
01:14:19,019 --> 01:14:21,988
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}就像把湿拖把放到范・戴恩太太床上
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Like putting the wet mop in Mrs. Van Daan's bed.

754
01:14:26,259 --> 01:14:28,921
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}现在又放到妈妈那里
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And now this with Mother.

755
01:14:28,995 --> 01:14:31,987
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我对自己说：“那是错误的。”
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I say to myself, "That was wrong."

756
01:14:32,065 --> 01:14:35,660
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}并且下决心再也不那么做了。再也不
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And I make up my mind I'm never going to do that again. Never.

757
01:14:37,337 --> 01:14:40,238
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我也许会做更坏的事情，但是绝不会做那件事
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I may do something worse, but I'll never do that again.

758
01:14:40,307 --> 01:14:44,641
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我也有好的地方，爸爸
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I have a nicer side, father.

759
01:14:44,711 --> 01:14:47,441
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}但是我害怕表现出来
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}But I'm scared to show it.

760
01:14:47,514 --> 01:14:50,847
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我怕大家会嘲笑我
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm afraid people will laugh at me.

761
01:14:52,385 --> 01:14:56,549
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}所以坏安妮来到外面......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}So the mean Anne comes to the outside...

762
01:14:56,623 --> 01:14:59,615
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}好安妮呆在里面......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}and the good Anne stays in the inside.

763
01:15:01,227 --> 01:15:05,095
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我也在一直努力改变......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And I keep on trying to switch them around...

764
01:15:05,165 --> 01:15:10,159
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}让好安妮在外面，把坏安妮留在里面
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}and have the good Anne outside and the bad Anne inside.

765
01:15:12,572 --> 01:15:14,904
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}那就是我要做的......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It would be what I'd like to be...

766
01:15:16,409 --> 01:15:20,641
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}或许......要是......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}and might be... if only...

767
01:15:42,769 --> 01:15:44,760
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}她睡着了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}She's asleep.

768
01:16:52,105 --> 01:16:57,543
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}1942年10月29日，星期四
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Thursday, the 29th of October, 1942.

769
01:16:57,610 --> 01:17:00,636
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}达索尔先生和我昨天大吵了一架
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Dussel and I had a great battle yesterday.

770
01:17:00,713 --> 01:17:04,274
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}是的，达索尔先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Yes, Mr. Dussel.

771
01:17:04,350 --> 01:17:08,514
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}在达索尔先生看来，没有，我在说一遍，我就没有任何可取之处
