772
01:17:10,356 --> 01:17:13,587
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}当他针对我的时候，我就想......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}While he was going on at me, I thought...

773
01:17:13,660 --> 01:17:17,221
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}总有一天，我要好好扇你.....
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"Someday, I'm going to give you such a smack...

774
01:17:17,297 --> 01:17:20,289
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}把你扇到棚顶去
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}that you'll fly right up to the ceiling. '"

775
01:17:22,135 --> 01:17:26,970
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}为什么所有大人都认为他知道怎样养大孩子？
