{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Particularly the grown-ups that haven't any.

777
01:17:39,319 --> 01:17:42,811
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}1942年11月9日，星期一
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Monday, the ninth of November, 1942.

778
01:17:42,889 --> 01:17:47,292
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}好消息。盟国在非洲登路了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Wonderful news. The Allies have landed in Africa.

779
01:17:47,360 --> 01:17:50,022
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}丘吉尔在伦敦BBC发表讲话
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Churchill spoke on the bbC from London.

780
01:17:50,096 --> 01:17:53,998
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他们常常给予别人的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Which they have so often meted out to others.

781
01:17:54,067 --> 01:17:57,230
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}这不是结束
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Ah, this is not the end.

782
01:17:57,303 --> 01:18:01,763
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}这甚至不是结束的开始
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}No, it is not even the beginning of the end.

783
01:18:01,841 --> 01:18:05,504
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}但这毕竟是开始的结束
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}But it is, perhaps, the end of the beginning.

784
01:18:05,578 --> 01:18:07,910
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}空袭越来越严重
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}The air raids are getting worse.

785
01:18:07,981 --> 01:18:11,382
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}英国飞机日夜飞往德国
