786
01:18:46,085 --> 01:18:49,577
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}太多了，太多了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It's too much. Just too much.

787
01:18:57,330 --> 01:18:59,992
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}要是他们炸到这所房子，我们该怎么办啊？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Suppose they hit this house? What will we do?

788
01:19:00,066 --> 01:19:03,729
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们不能到街上去。我们该怎么办啊？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We can't go out in the street. What will we do?

789
01:19:03,803 --> 01:19:08,754
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}要是他们炸到这所房子，你的烦恼就解决了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}If they hit this house, your worries will be over.

790
01:19:12,425 --> 01:19:15,588
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}那个噪音――爆炸声――他们击中英国飞机了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}That noise--that big explosion--they hit one of the English planes.

791
01:19:15,661 --> 01:19:17,424
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-正好落在这个街区。  -彼得
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- It fell right in this block. - Peter!

792
01:19:20,533 --> 01:19:22,865
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}彼得！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Peter!

793
01:19:33,679 --> 01:19:36,614
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-离这儿很远。  -不要紧张
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-It's far away from here. - Don't be nervous.

794
01:19:36,682 --> 01:19:40,140
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}看着吧。嗨，范・戴恩太太，对你来说，这就像音乐吧
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Just look at them. Why, Mrs. Van Daan, this should be music to your ears.

795
01:19:40,219 --> 01:19:42,153
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-音乐？  -当然
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Music?  - Of course.

796
01:19:42,221 --> 01:19:44,451
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}英国派来的飞机越多......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}The more planes the British send over...

797
01:19:44,524 --> 01:19:47,516
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}战争就结束的越快，我们也就能越快从这出去回家
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}the sooner the war will be over, the sooner we'll be out of here and home.

798
01:19:47,593 --> 01:19:49,720
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我都不相信战争会结束
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I don't believe it'll ever be over.

799
01:19:51,430 --> 01:19:54,524
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你知道我现在需要的吗？一杯茶
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You know what I'd like right now? A cup of tea.

800
01:19:54,600 --> 01:19:56,727
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}哦，是的，请
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Oh, yes, please.

801
01:19:56,802 --> 01:19:58,929
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你不能喝早餐的茶
