{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}是烟叶，真的是
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It's tobacco. Really, it is.

891
01:26:04,451 --> 01:26:07,443
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}里面有一点绒毛，但是不多
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}There's a little fluff in it, but not much.

892
01:26:14,828 --> 01:26:17,991
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-点着了！  -看他！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- It works! -Look at him.

893
01:26:20,000 --> 01:26:21,991
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}谢谢你，安妮。谢谢
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Thank you, Anne. Thank you.

894
01:26:25,472 --> 01:26:27,702
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}范・戴恩先生！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Van Daan!

895
01:26:29,976 --> 01:26:32,444
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}爸爸的。光明节的问候
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}For Mother. Hanukkah greeting.

896
01:26:34,114 --> 01:26:37,447
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}这里有个我要支付的借据
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"Here's an I.O.U. that I promise to pay.

897
01:26:37,517 --> 01:26:43,353
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}“做十个小时你吩咐我做的任何事情
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"Ten hours of doing... whatever you say.

898
01:26:43,423 --> 01:26:45,914
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}签名，安妮・弗兰克。”
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Signed, Anne Frank."

899
01:26:52,999 --> 01:26:55,297
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}十个小时任何要你做的事情？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Ten hours of doing what you're told?

900
01:26:55,368 --> 01:26:57,632
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-任何要你做的事情？  -对
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Anything you're told? - That's right.

901
01:27:00,840 --> 01:27:03,832
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你不会要把它卖了吧，弗兰克太太，是吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You wouldn't want to sell that, Mrs. Frank, would you?

902
01:27:03,910 --> 01:27:07,710
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}绝不会。这是我得到的最珍贵的礼物
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Never. This is the most precious gift I've ever had.

903
01:27:10,016 --> 01:27:15,454
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-给爸爸。  -我没想到还能得到礼物
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- For father. - I wasn't supposed to have a present.

904
01:27:15,522 --> 01:27:17,581
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-看。   -是条围巾
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Look at that. - It's a muffler.

905
01:27:17,657 --> 01:27:20,990
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-哦，知道。   -象领带那样围在脖子上
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-Oh, I know. -To wear around your neck like an ascot.

906
01:27:23,330 --> 01:27:25,418
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我每天晚上在黑暗中织的。我恐怕在黑暗中会更好看
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I knitted it in the dark each night. I'm afraid it looks better in the dark.

907
01:27:28,488 --> 01:27:31,013
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}真漂亮。谢谢，安妮。谢谢
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It's fine. Thank you, Annele. Thank you.

908
01:27:31,091 --> 01:27:34,754
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-太漂亮了。  -好可爱，不是吗？谢谢，安妮
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Isn't it beautiful. - Lovely, huh? Thank you, Anne.

909
01:27:38,431 --> 01:27:43,266
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-给毛刺的。  -他一定会喜欢
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- For Mouschi. -He'll like it.

910
01:27:44,604 --> 01:27:50,304
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}这是给你的。你自己的，来自呱呱小姐
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And this is for you. Yourself. From Miss Quack-Quack.

911
01:27:52,178 --> 01:27:54,043
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}快，打开
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Go on. Open it.

912
01:27:54,114 --> 01:27:57,777
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不想打开吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Aren't you going to open it?

913
01:28:00,153 --> 01:28:04,783
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-给我们看看是什么。  -是个安全剃须刀
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-Show us what it is. - It's a safety razor.

914
01:28:04,858 --> 01:28:09,192
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不是新的。米耶普给我弄的二手货。你的确需要有个剃须刀
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It's not new. Miep got it for me second-hand. But you do need a razor.

915
01:28:10,630 --> 01:28:15,795
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-用来做什么？  -看他的上唇。看到没有？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- What for? - Look at his upper lip. See?

916
01:28:15,869 --> 01:28:17,962
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他要刮掉吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He wants to get rid of that?

917
01:28:18,037 --> 01:28:21,302
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}上面涂些牛奶，让你的猫舔掉
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Put some milk on it and let the cat lick it off.

918
01:28:23,109 --> 01:28:25,168
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你认为很可笑，是吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You think you're funny, don't you?

919
01:28:25,245 --> 01:28:28,737
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}看，他都等不及了。他现在就要去试试
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Look, he can't wait. He's going in to try it now.

920
01:28:28,815 --> 01:28:31,807
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我要把礼物给毛刺
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm going to give Mouschi his present.

921
01:28:31,885 --> 01:28:34,877
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-毛刺，毛刺，毛刺。  -够了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Mouschi, Mouschi, Mouschi. - Enough.

922
01:28:34,954 --> 01:28:39,288
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}最后，却不是最少，给我的室友，达索尔先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And last, but never least, my roommate, Mr. Dussel.

923
01:28:39,359 --> 01:28:41,691
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}有东西给我？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Something for me?

924
01:28:48,435 --> 01:28:51,927
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-胶囊。  -是耳塞，塞到你的耳朵里......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Capsules. - They're earplugs to put in your ears...

925
01:28:52,005 --> 01:28:54,735
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}那样晚上我折腾的时候，你就听不见了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}so you won't hear me when I thrash around at night.

926
01:28:54,808 --> 01:28:58,471
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我自己做的，试一下，看能不能听到我
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I made them myself. Try them. See if you can hear me.

927
01:29:03,082 --> 01:29:05,642
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}等我塞进去――这样吗？你是这意思吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Wait, I'll put-- Like that? Is that what you mean?

928
01:29:05,718 --> 01:29:07,777
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-准备好了吗？  -什么？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Are you ready? - What?

929
01:29:07,854 --> 01:29:13,087
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-准备好了吗？  -好使了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Are you ready? - They work.

930
01:29:19,032 --> 01:29:22,297
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}出不来了。出不来了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}They went in. They went in.

931
01:29:22,368 --> 01:29:25,132
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他拿不出来了。你怎么了？拿出来
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He can't get 'em out. What's the matter with you? Get 'em out.

932
01:29:25,205 --> 01:29:27,366
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}把耳塞拿出来
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Take 'em out.

933
01:29:27,440 --> 01:29:29,431
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}拿出来了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I got 'em.

934
01:29:30,710 --> 01:29:35,443
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}谢谢你
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Thank you.

935
01:29:35,515 --> 01:29:38,177
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}现在让我们唱一首歌吧，爸爸
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And now let's sing the song, father.

936
01:29:38,251 --> 01:29:41,084
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}等等，你就要听到光明节颂歌了，达索尔先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Wait till you hear the Hanukkah song, Mr. Dussel.

937
01:29:44,157 --> 01:29:46,489
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}安妮，我们今晚不该唱歌
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Annele, we shouldn't sing the song tonight.

938
01:29:46,559 --> 01:29:49,892
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你看，达索尔先生，那是一首喜悦，欢乐之歌
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You see, Mr. Dussel, it's a song of jubilation and of rejoicing.

939
01:29:49,963 --> 01:29:52,454
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}人啊，太真容易对那种事情兴致勃勃了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}One is apt to become just a little too enthusiastic about it.

940
01:29:52,532 --> 01:29:55,126
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}求你，爸爸，让我们唱颂歌吧。我保证不喊
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Please, let's sing the song, father. I promise not to shout.

941
01:29:55,201 --> 01:29:58,466
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-好吧，不过要小声，安妮。  -哦！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Very well, but quietly, Anne. - Oh!

942
01:29:58,538 --> 01:30:03,032
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}哦！我告诉过你不要带猫过来
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Oh! I told you not to come in here with that cat.

943
01:30:03,109 --> 01:30:06,875
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}出去
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Get out of here.

944
01:30:06,946 --> 01:30:10,109
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你怎么了？难道你没有感觉吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}What's the matter with you? Haven't you any sense?

945
01:30:10,183 --> 01:30:12,777
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-把猫弄出去。  -猫？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Get that cat out of here. - Cat?

946
01:30:12,852 --> 01:30:16,686
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}听着，把它弄出去！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You heard me. Get it out of here!

947
01:30:18,057 --> 01:30:20,821
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我没有猫
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I have no cat.

948
01:30:20,894 --> 01:30:23,328
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}达索尔先生！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Dussel!

949
01:30:23,396 --> 01:30:26,160
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不必是猫本身
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It doesn't have to be the cat.

950
01:30:26,232 --> 01:30:29,895
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}仅仅猫身上的毛就足够了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Just the hairs on his clothing from the cat is enough.

951
01:30:29,969 --> 01:30:33,234
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-当他进来的时候......  -不要再烦人了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- When he comes in the room...  - You won't be bothered anymore.

952
01:30:33,306 --> 01:30:36,400
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-我们必须摆脱它。  -最后，你听我说
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- We're getting rid of it. - At last, you listen to me.

953
01:30:36,476 --> 01:30:40,139
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我并不是替你说话。都是你自己认为的，都是
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm not doing it for you. That's all in your mind. All of it.

954
01:30:40,213 --> 01:30:44,513
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我那么做是因为，看到那只猫吃掉所有我们的食物，我很恼火
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm doing it because I'm sick of seeing that cat eat all our food.

955
01:30:44,584 --> 01:30:46,518
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不对。我只是喂它残渣剩饭
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}That's not true. I only give him scraps.

956
01:30:46,586 --> 01:30:51,080
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}得了。它天天在胖
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Don't tell me. He gets fatter every day.

957
01:30:51,157 --> 01:30:54,285
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}该死的猫看起来比我们过的都好。今晚让它滚出去
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Damn cat looks better than any of us. Out he goes tonight.

958
01:30:54,360 --> 01:30:57,523
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-不！  -范・戴恩先生，你不能那么做
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- No! - Mr. Van Daan, you can't do that.

959
01:30:57,597 --> 01:30:59,997
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}那是彼得的猫。彼得爱他的猫
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}That's Peter's cat. Peter loves that cat.

960
01:31:00,066 --> 01:31:01,431
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}安妮
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Anne.

961
01:31:02,835 --> 01:31:06,737
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-要是他走，我也走。  -走，走
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- If he goes, I go. - Go. Go.

962
01:31:06,806 --> 01:31:09,468
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他不会走，猫也不用走。你怎么了？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He's not going, and the cat's not going. What's the matter with you?

963
01:31:09,542 --> 01:31:13,603
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}光明节。光明节，来，安妮，唱歌
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It's Hanukkah. It's Hanukkah. Please, Anne, sing.

964
01:31:17,550 --> 01:31:19,677
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}安妮
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Annele.

965
01:31:19,752 --> 01:31:22,516
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我想我们应该先把蜡烛吹灭
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I think we should first blow out the candles.

966
01:31:22,589 --> 01:31:24,523
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}那样明晚还会有东西了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Then we'll have something for tomorrow night.

967
01:31:24,591 --> 01:31:28,584
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}爸爸，你应该让蜡烛自己点完
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}father, you're supposed to let it burn itself out.

968
01:31:28,661 --> 01:31:31,596
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我肯定上帝会理解我们的窘迫的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm sure that God understands shortages.

969
01:31:31,664 --> 01:31:33,598
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}赞美我主，供养我们......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Praise be Thou, O Lord our God, who has sustained us...

970
01:31:33,666 --> 01:31:35,998
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}允许我们欢庆这快乐的节日
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}and permitted us to celebrate this joyous festival.

971
01:31:36,069 --> 01:31:38,003
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-阿门。  -阿门
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Amen. -Amen.

972
01:35:17,556 --> 01:35:21,219
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-我想他们走了。 -他们发现我们了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- I think they've gone. - They found us.

973
01:35:21,293 --> 01:35:23,488
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}要是发现了，他们现在就已经上来了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}If they had, they would be up here by now.

974
01:35:23,562 --> 01:35:28,056
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我知道那一定是环保警察。他们去找帮手了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I know it was the Green Police. They've gone to get help.

975
01:35:28,134 --> 01:35:30,364
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}或许是盖世太保，在找文件
