01:35:30,436 --> 01:35:34,532
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}或者是另一个窃贼在找钱
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Or another thief looking for money.

977
01:35:40,813 --> 01:35:43,475
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我下去
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm going down.

978
01:35:43,549 --> 01:35:47,007
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-他们可能还在那儿。  -安妮，今天是星期六
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- They may still be there. - Annele, this is Saturday.

979
01:35:47,086 --> 01:35:49,452
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们没办法知道下面发生什么了......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We have no way of knowing what has happened down there...

980
01:35:49,522 --> 01:35:51,456
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}等米耶普和卡勒先生来了才能知道
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}until Miep and Mr. Kraler come.

981
01:35:51,524 --> 01:35:55,517
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们不能活在茫然未知中。现在，让我去看看
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We cannot live with this uncertainty. Now, please. Please.

982
01:36:17,483 --> 01:36:20,919
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}拿我们的钱来。他们说你可以买通他们。这么多钱买一条命不少了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Get our money. They say you can buy them off. So much a head.

983
01:36:20,986 --> 01:36:23,454
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-快，上楼拿钱。  -安静
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Quick, go upstairs and get the money. - Keep still.

984
01:36:23,522 --> 01:36:26,889
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你想被拖到集中营去吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You wanna be dragged off to a concentration camp?

985
01:36:26,959 --> 01:36:29,018
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你想站在这，直到他们来带走你吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You gonna stand there until they come up here and get you?

986
01:36:29,095 --> 01:36:31,086
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}安静行不？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Will you keep still!

987
01:36:48,881 --> 01:36:51,475
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}有人来了，让爸爸回来
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Someone go and make father come back.

988
01:37:01,494 --> 01:37:04,986
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-你还没做够吗？  -不要这样，范・戴恩先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Haven't you done enough? - Please, Mr. Van Daan.

989
01:37:10,569 --> 01:37:12,662
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-安妮。  -嘘
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Anne! - Shh.

990
01:37:31,590 --> 01:37:36,584
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我要向山举目。我的帮助从何而来
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I lift up mine eyes unto the mountains from whence cometh my help.

991
01:37:36,662 --> 01:37:39,995
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我的帮助从造天地的上帝而来
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}My help cometh from the Lord who made heaven and Earth.

992
01:38:18,710 --> 01:38:21,702
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}保护你的必不打盹
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He that keepeth thee will not slumber.

993
01:38:21,780 --> 01:38:26,012
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}保护以色列的，也不打盹，也不睡觉
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He that keepeth Israel doth neither slumber nor sleep.

994
01:38:26,084 --> 01:38:30,248
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}保护你的是上帝。上帝的荫庇来自......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}The Lord is thy keeper. The Lord is thy shade from--

995
01:38:44,970 --> 01:38:48,303
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}No.

996
01:39:14,867 --> 01:39:18,496
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-我最好去看看，确定一下。  -呀
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- I better go and look and make sure. - Ja.

997
01:39:31,283 --> 01:39:35,049
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}祈求我主保佑你远离邪恶
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Pray that the Lord shall keep thee from all evil.

998
01:39:35,120 --> 01:39:38,385
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-保佑你的灵魂。  -请聆听我的祈祷，哦，以色列
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- He shall keep thy soul. - Hear me, O Israel.

999
01:39:38,457 --> 01:39:41,449
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我主将荫庇你的出入
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}The Lord shall guard thy going out and thy coming in.

1000
01:39:48,500 --> 01:39:51,128
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他带着打字机匆忙跑了......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He took the typewriter and ran away in such a hurry...

1001
01:39:51,203 --> 01:39:53,728
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他没关大门――还敞着呢
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}he didn't stop to shut the street door-- it was swinging wide open.

1002
01:39:53,805 --> 01:39:56,205
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}一个更夫过来了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}A watchman was passing.

1003
01:40:42,187 --> 01:40:45,054
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}看，工具
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Look. Tools.

1004
01:44:34,886 --> 01:44:37,047
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}呀
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Ja.

1005
01:44:37,122 --> 01:44:42,788
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}妙-妙-妙. 妙-妙-妙，妙，妙
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Meetz-meetz-meetz. Meetz-meetz-meetz. Meow, meow.

1006
01:44:42,861 --> 01:44:46,456
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他们失窃了。他听到我来就出去了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}They had a burglary. He got out as he heard me coming.

1007
01:44:49,467 --> 01:44:54,461
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}妙-妙，妙-妙
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Meetz-meetz，Meetz-meetz.

1008
01:45:12,891 --> 01:45:16,657
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我要锁上门去报告
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I will lock the door and report it.

1009
01:45:25,604 --> 01:45:28,198
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他们走了。他们把门锁上了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}They've gone. They've locked the door.

1010
01:45:28,273 --> 01:45:30,036
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}感谢上帝他们走了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Thank God they've gone.

1011
01:45:30,075 --> 01:45:31,349
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我宁愿他们带走我们，而不继续忍受这个可怕的痛苦
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'd just as soon they'd take us than to continue with this terrible agony.

1012
01:45:31,349 --> 01:45:34,341
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我宁愿他们带走我们，而不继续忍受这个可怕的痛苦
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'd just as soon they'd take us than to continue with this terrible agony.

1013
01:45:34,419 --> 01:45:37,286
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-我受不了了。  -没事了，安妮
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- I can't stand it. - It's all right, Annele.

1014
01:45:37,355 --> 01:45:41,155
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-危险过去了。  -谁说危险过去了？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- The danger has passed. - Who says the danger is passed?

1015
01:45:41,226 --> 01:45:44,218
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你没意识到我们比过去更危险了吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Don't you realize that we're in greater danger than ever?

1016
01:45:44,295 --> 01:45:46,456
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}哦，达索尔先生，能安静一下吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Please, Mr. Dussel, will you keep still.

1017
01:45:46,531 --> 01:45:50,524
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}因为这个笨蛋，人们现在知道我们在这里了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Thanks to this clumsy fool, someone now knows we're up here.

1018
01:45:50,602 --> 01:45:53,765
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-人们知道我们藏在这里。  -是个窃贼
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Someone knows we're up here hiding. - It's a thief.

1019
01:45:53,838 --> 01:45:55,772
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你想那个窃贼会不会去环保警察那里报告......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You think the thief is going to go to the Green Police and say...

1020
01:45:55,840 --> 01:45:58,934
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}“我某个夜里在一个地方偷东西，听到我头上有声音”?
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}"I was robbing a place the other night, and I heard a noise above my head"?

1021
01:45:59,010 --> 01:46:01,308
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-你认为一个窃贼会那么做吗？  -会的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- You think a thief is going to do that? - Yes, he will.

1022
01:46:01,379 --> 01:46:05,577
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-你疯了。  -总有一天窃贼会被抓住
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- You're crazy. - Someday the thief will be caught.

1023
01:46:05,650 --> 01:46:08,483
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他会和盖世太保做笔交易
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He'll make a bargain with the Gestapo.

1024
01:46:08,553 --> 01:46:11,283
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他会和盖世太保说：“要是你放了我......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He'll say to the Gestapo, "If you let me off...

1025
01:46:11,356 --> 01:46:13,483
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我会告诉你那些犹太人藏在哪里。”
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'll show you where some Jews are hiding."

1026
01:46:13,558 --> 01:46:15,719
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-我就这么认为。  -噢！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- That's what I think. - Oy!

1027
01:46:15,793 --> 01:46:19,058
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-他说的对。  -哦，妈妈，让我们离开这里吧
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- He's right. - Oh, Mother, let's get out of here.

1028
01:46:19,130 --> 01:46:23,089
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-我们不能住在这里了。  -求你，让我们走
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- We can't stay here now. - Please, let's go.

1029
01:46:23,168 --> 01:46:25,659
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}走？去哪儿？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Go? Where?

1030
01:46:29,874 --> 01:46:32,274
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}是啊，去哪儿？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Yes, where?

1031
01:46:33,912 --> 01:46:35,903
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们都失去信心了吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Have we lost all faith?

1032
01:46:36,981 --> 01:46:39,245
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}所有的勇气？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}All courage?

1033
01:46:39,317 --> 01:46:42,309
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}几个月前，我们认为他们会来抓我们，不是吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}A few moments ago, we thought they had come for us, didn't we?

1034
01:46:42,387 --> 01:46:47,552
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们认为都完了。你看，并没有完，我们还活着。我们很安全
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We thought it was the end. Well, it was not the end. We are alive. We are safe.

1035
01:46:47,625 --> 01:46:50,924
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}感谢我主，你无边的仁慈......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We thank Thee, O Lord, our God, that in Thy infinite mercy...

1036
01:46:50,995 --> 01:46:53,828
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}再次赐予我们安适
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Thou hast again seen fit to spare us.

1037
01:46:53,898 --> 01:46:56,560
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-阿门。  -阿门
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Amen. - Amen.

1038
01:47:01,573 --> 01:47:04,064
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}安妮
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Annele.

1039
01:47:04,142 --> 01:47:06,133
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}颂歌，啊？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}The song, hmm?

1040
01:47:07,612 --> 01:47:09,603
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}唱颂歌怎么样？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}How about the song?

1041
01:47:59,564 --> 01:48:02,000
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}光明节快乐
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Happy Hanukkah.

1042
01:48:02,000 --> 01:48:02,625
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}光明节快乐
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Happy Hanukkah.

1043
01:48:38,828 --> 01:48:44,323
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}1944年1月1日，星期六
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Saturday, the first of January, 1944.

1044
01:48:44,401 --> 01:48:46,835
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}又一个新年到来了......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Another new year has begun...

1045
01:48:46,903 --> 01:48:49,736
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们发觉我们还藏在这里
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}and we find ourselves still in our hiding place.

1046
01:48:54,911 --> 01:49:00,247
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们藏在这里已经一年五个月零二十五天了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We have been here now for one year, five months and 25 days.

1047
01:49:02,752 --> 01:49:06,415
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}其中一个成员离开了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}One of our family has left us.

1048
01:49:06,489 --> 01:49:10,789
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}毛刺跑掉了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mouschi ran away.

1049
01:49:10,860 --> 01:49:13,852
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们都消瘦了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We're all a little thinner.

1050
01:49:13,930 --> 01:49:18,367
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}范・戴恩先生的各种议论还是象过去一样猛烈
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}The Van Daans'discussions are as violent as ever.

1051
01:49:18,435 --> 01:49:24,271
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}妈妈仍然不理解我，不过我也一样不理解她
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mother still doesn't understand me, but then, I don't understand her either.

1052
01:49:28,445 --> 01:49:33,280
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}然而，有一个很大的变化，我自己的变化
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}There is one great change, however. A change in myself.

1053
01:49:35,151 --> 01:49:40,646
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我曾经在哪里读到过，象我这个年龄的女孩，总是感觉......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I read somewhere that girls of my age don't feel quite certain of themselves...

1054
01:49:40,724 --> 01:49:42,715
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}在内心深处变得不安分......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}that they become quiet within...

1055
01:49:42,792 --> 01:49:46,626
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}并且开始想着在身体中发生的奇迹
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}and begin to think of the miracle that is taking place in their bodies.

1056
01:49:48,932 --> 01:49:53,426
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我想我身上发生的一切都太美妙了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I think that what is happening to me is so wonderful.

1057
01:49:53,503 --> 01:49:58,668
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不仅仅是外表能看到的，还有内在发生的一切
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Not only what can be seen, but what is taking place inside.

1058
01:50:00,410 --> 01:50:05,404
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}每次变化发生的时候，我就拥有了一个甜蜜的秘密......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Each time it has happened, I feel I have a sweet secret...

1059
01:50:05,482 --> 01:50:10,476
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我渴望再次感觉到秘密的时刻
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}and I long for the time when I shall feel that secret within me again.

1060
01:51:59,262 --> 01:52:02,754
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}安妮，彼得
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Annele. Peter.

1061
