02:06:59,488 --> 02:07:02,423
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他整天自己占着房间
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He takes the room for himself the entire day.

1264
02:07:02,491 --> 02:07:05,324
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你不打算今晚再去见彼得吗，嗯？
