{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm sorry, Mother. I'm going to Peter's room.

1274
02:07:38,193 --> 02:07:41,492
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我可不想让彼得罗妮拉・范・戴恩毁了我们的友谊
