1275
02:07:47,869 --> 02:07:49,962
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}稍等，达索尔先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Just a moment, Mr. Dussel.

1276
02:07:52,841 --> 02:07:55,309
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}在我那时候都是男孩拜访女孩的
