{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你是不是已经改变了对我的看法......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Did you change your mind...

1419
02:18:21,352 --> 02:18:23,786
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}就像我改变了对你的看法一样？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}the way I changed my mind about you?

1420
02:18:25,589 --> 02:18:28,080
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}噢，你会知道的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Well, you'll see.

1421
02:19:47,838 --> 02:19:49,829
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}晚安，安妮
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Good night, Annele.

1422
02:19:55,112 --> 02:19:57,103
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-晚安，天使。  -晚安
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Good night, angel. - Good night.

1423
02:20:23,641 --> 02:20:25,575
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}啊哈
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mm-hmm.

1424
02:20:38,389 --> 02:20:41,051
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}在外面弥漫着静悄悄的兴奋
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Outside there is a quiet excitement.

1425
02:20:41,125 --> 02:20:44,185
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}盟军占领症的热度也一天天在这里升高
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Invasion fever is mounting from day to day.

1426
02:20:44,261 --> 02:20:47,287
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}人们除了谈论解放的希望，什么也不说了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And people talk of nothing else but the hope of liberation.

1427
02:20:48,299 --> 02:20:50,233
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}解放最好快点到来
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It had best come soon.

1428
02:20:50,301 --> 02:20:52,769
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们也有坏消息
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We here have had bad news.

1429
02:20:52,837 --> 02:20:56,739
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}给米耶普提供定量供应证的人被捕了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}The people from whom Miep got our ration cards have been arrested.

1430
02:20:58,956 --> 02:21:02,084
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}卡勒先生住院了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Kraler is in the hospital.

1431
02:21:02,159 --> 02:21:04,821
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}好像他得了溃疡
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It seems he has ulcers.

1432
02:21:04,895 --> 02:21:07,386
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我恐怕我们就是他的溃疡
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm afraid we are his ulcers.

1433
02:21:08,599 --> 02:21:11,193
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}米耶普得处理公事，还得照看我们
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Miep has to run the business and us too.

1434
02:21:13,437 --> 02:21:15,496
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们真的太幸运了......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}How very fortunate we are...

1435
02:21:15,572 --> 02:21:18,268
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}当想到外面发生的一切的时候
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}when you think of what is happening outside.

1436
02:22:18,535 --> 02:22:20,969
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我感觉春天正在到来
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I feel that spring is coming.

1437
02:22:22,039 --> 02:22:24,769
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我感觉春天充满了我的身体和灵魂
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I feel it in my whole body and soul.

1438
02:22:26,009 --> 02:22:28,102
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我彻底迷茫了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'm utterly confused.

1439
02:22:30,047 --> 02:22:34,040
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我一直渴望...渴望着一切
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I am longing...so longing for everything.

1440
02:25:18,248 --> 02:25:21,308
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}奥托！奥托，快。他在偷食物
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Otto! Otto, quick. He's stealing the food!

1441
02:25:21,385 --> 02:25:23,580
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-埃蒂茨，埃蒂茨！  -范・戴恩先生，让我看看！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Edith, Edith! - Mr. Van Daan, let me see that!

1442
02:25:23,653 --> 02:25:26,144
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}范・戴恩先生，过来...... 让我......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Van Daan, come... Let me...

1443
02:25:26,223 --> 02:25:29,283
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-给我......  -发生什么事了？范・戴恩先生。范......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Give me... - What happened? Mr. Van Daan. Mr....

1444
02:25:29,359 --> 02:25:31,293
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}看，面包！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Look, the bread!

1445
02:25:31,361 --> 02:25:33,295
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你这个肮脏的贼
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You dirty thief.

1446
02:25:33,363 --> 02:25:36,093
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-你这个废物。 -放开他。救救我，彼得
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- You good-for-nothing. - Let him go. Help me, Peter.

1447
02:25:36,166 --> 02:25:38,691
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}放开他！彼得，救救我！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Let him go! Peter, help me!

1448
02:25:38,769 --> 02:25:41,670
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}放开他！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Let him go!

1449
02:25:52,749 --> 02:25:55,343
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}普提，那是什么？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Putti, what is it?

1450
02:25:55,419 --> 02:25:58,354
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他在偷面包
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He was stealing the bread.

1451
02:25:58,422 --> 02:26:02,688
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}是你啊。我们还都一直以为是老鼠偷的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It was you. And all the time we thought it was the rats.

1452
02:26:02,759 --> 02:26:05,523
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}范・戴恩先生，你怎么能这样？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Van Daan, how could you?

1453
02:26:06,797 --> 02:26:10,289
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-我饿啊。  -我们都饿
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- I'm hungry. - We're all of us hungry.

1454
02:26:10,367 --> 02:26:13,564
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我看着孩子们越来越瘦
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I see the children getting thinner and thinner.

1455
02:26:13,637 --> 02:26:17,471
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你自己的儿子，我听到他在梦中呻吟，他太饿了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Your own son, I've heard him moan in his sleep, he's so hungry.

1456
02:26:17,541 --> 02:26:22,342
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你却下来偷食物，那些应该给孩子们的食物
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And you come down and steal food that should go to them, the children.

1457
02:26:24,548 --> 02:26:26,675
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他比我们需要更多的食物
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He needs more food than the rest of us.

1458
02:26:26,750 --> 02:26:29,184
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他吃得多，他太胖了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He's used to more. He's a big man.

1459
02:26:29,252 --> 02:26:31,345
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And you!

1460
02:26:31,421 --> 02:26:34,049
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你比他更坏。你是一个母亲
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You're worse than he is. You're a mother.

1461
02:26:34,124 --> 02:26:37,025
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}为了这个人，你竟然牺牲你自己的儿子，这个......这个......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And yet you sacrifice your son to this man, this...this...

1462
02:26:37,094 --> 02:26:39,028
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}埃蒂茨
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Edith.

1463
02:26:39,096 --> 02:26:41,121
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}别以为我没看到你
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Don't think I haven't seen you.

1464
02:26:41,198 --> 02:26:44,998
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}总是挑出最好的那点留给他。我一直盯着你呢
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Always saving the choicest bits for him. I've watched you.

1465
02:26:45,068 --> 02:26:47,901
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}多少天了，我忍着没说，现在不忍了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Day after day, and I've held my tongue, but not any longer.

1466
02:26:47,971 --> 02:26:49,905
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}以后再也不忍了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Not after this!

1467
02:26:49,973 --> 02:26:53,340
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}现在我要他离开。我要他从这里出去
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Now I want him to go. I want him to get out of here!

1468
02:26:53,410 --> 02:26:55,344
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}埃蒂茨
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Edith.

1469
02:26:55,412 --> 02:26:57,903
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}从这出去？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Get out of here?

1470
02:26:59,382 --> 02:27:02,715
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-你是什么意思？  -就这样，拿着你的东西，出去
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- What do you mean? -Just that. Take your things. Get out.

1471
02:27:02,786 --> 02:27:05,755
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你在说气话。你不是那意思
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You're speaking in anger. You cannot mean what you're saying.

1472
02:27:05,822 --> 02:27:09,417
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-就是那意思。  -两年了，我们生活在一起
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-I mean exactly that. -For 2 years we have lived side by side.

1473
02:27:09,493 --> 02:27:11,552
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们尊重彼此的权利
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We have respected each other's rights.

1474
02:27:11,628 --> 02:27:14,563
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们努力和平相处。我们现在要全都丢弃吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We have managed to live in peace. Are we going to throw it all away?

1475
02:27:16,666 --> 02:27:18,657
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}范・戴恩先生......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Van Daan...

1476
02:27:18,735 --> 02:27:21,499
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我知道这种事再也不会发生了。是不是？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I know this is never going to happen again, is it?

1477
02:27:21,571 --> 02:27:25,473
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-不会了，不会了  -哈，偷一次，还会偷第二次
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- No, no. - Ah, he steals once, he'll steal again.

1478
02:27:25,542 --> 02:27:28,511
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我要他们离开。现在就走
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I want them to leave. You go now!

1479
02:27:36,186 --> 02:27:38,120
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}妈妈
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mother.

1480
02:27:38,188 --> 02:27:41,885
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你要把彼得也撵出去？他什么也没做啊
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You're not putting Peter out? Peter hasn't done anything.

1481
02:27:41,958 --> 02:27:45,121
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我不是说彼得。他可以呆在这里
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I don't mean Peter. Peter can stay.

1482
02:27:45,195 --> 02:27:48,460
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}要是他走我也得走。他是我爸爸
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'll have to go if he goes. That's my father.

1483
02:27:48,532 --> 02:27:51,000
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他不配做你爸爸，那个人
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He's no father to you, that man.

1484
02:27:51,067 --> 02:27:53,194
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他不知道爸爸意味着什么
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He doesn't know what it means to be a father.

1485
02:27:53,270 --> 02:27:55,966
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}感觉不合适。我不能留在这
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I wouldn't feel right. I couldn't stay.

1486
02:27:56,039 --> 02:27:58,132
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}那么好吧
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Very well then.

1487
02:27:58,208 --> 02:28:00,142
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}彼得，不
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Peter. No.

1488
02:28:03,647 --> 02:28:08,016
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}弗兰克太太，你要把我们赶到大街上吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mrs. Frank, you would put us out in the street?

1489
02:28:09,286 --> 02:28:11,254
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你们可以再找一个藏身之处
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You can find another hiding place.

1490
02:28:12,522 --> 02:28:16,322
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们去哪里找一个地窖......一个壁橱啊？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Where would we even find a cellar... a-a closet?

1491
02:28:22,899 --> 02:28:24,833
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}弗兰克先生......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Frank...

1492
02:28:27,704 --> 02:28:29,865
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你告诉普提......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}you told Putti...

1493
02:28:29,940 --> 02:28:34,274
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你不会忘了吧，当你刚来到荷兰的时候，他是怎么对你的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}you would never forget what he did for you when you first came to Holland.

1494
02:28:34,344 --> 02:28:36,608
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你说过你永远都报答不了他
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You said you never would be able to repay him.

1495
02:28:36,680 --> 02:28:40,275
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}要是我丈夫有什么欠你的，他已经加倍偿还了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}If my husband had any obligations to you, he has paid it over and over.

1496
02:28:40,350 --> 02:28:43,877
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}埃蒂茨，我不明白。我从来没见你这样
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Edith, I don't know you. I've never seen you like this.

1497
02:28:43,954 --> 02:28:46,479
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我早就该说出来了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I should have spoken out long ago.

1498
02:28:46,556 --> 02:28:48,717
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你对有些人没好处
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You can't be nice to some people.

1499
02:28:48,792 --> 02:28:51,886
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}如果你不来这，本来我们会有足够的东西
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}There would have been plenty for all of us if you hadn't come in here!

1500
02:28:51,962 --> 02:28:55,090
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不，不，范・戴恩太太。
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}No, no, Mrs. Van Daan. Please.

1501
02:28:59,102 --> 02:29:02,469
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们不必纳粹毁掉我们了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We don't need the Nazis to destroy us.

1502
02:29:02,539 --> 02:29:05,064
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们自己就毁掉自己了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We're destroying ourselves.

1503
02:29:10,180 --> 02:29:13,149
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}妈妈，请不要让他们离开
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mother, please don't send them away.

1504
02:29:13,216 --> 02:29:16,549
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-已经天亮了。  -他们会被抓住的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- It's daylight. - And they'll be caught.

1505
02:29:18,054 --> 02:29:20,522
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-最高统帅部......  -他们现在不用走
