1598
02:36:39,799 --> 02:36:43,394
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他今天被抓住藏了两个犹太人
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He was picked up today for hiding two Jews in his house.

1599
02:36:51,110 --> 02:36:53,237
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}没有太多消息
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}There's not much.

1600
02:36:53,312 --> 02:36:56,042
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}那是我们的蔬菜商，豪克先生，他们被捕了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It was Mr. Hauk, our greengrocer, they arrested.

1601
02:36:58,017 --> 02:36:59,951
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}另外一个消息是......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And the other news is...

1602
02:37:00,019 --> 02:37:02,579
