{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}the Gestapo have found our typewriter that was stolen.

1603
02:37:02,655 --> 02:37:04,885
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-不。  -啊哈
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- No. - Uh-huh.

1604
02:37:04,957 --> 02:37:09,121
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他们会去找打字机，然后找到我们
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}They'll trace it back and back till it gets to us.

1605
02:37:09,161 --> 02:37:10,432
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你瞧吧，你......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You watch, you...

1606
02:37:10,432 --> 02:37:11,421
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你瞧吧，你......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You watch, you...

1607
02:37:24,813 --> 02:37:26,974
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}每个人都情绪低落
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Everyone is low.

1608
02:37:27,049 --> 02:37:29,381
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}就是爸爸也提不起精神
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Even father can't raise their spirits.

1609
02:37:30,686 --> 02:37:33,519
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我常常会沮丧......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I have often been downcast myself...

1610
02:37:33,589 --> 02:37:35,580
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不过从没绝望
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}but never in despair.

1611
02:37:35,657 --> 02:37:40,253
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}当我写字的时候，就会忘掉一切，但是......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I can shake oFF everything if I write, but--

1612
02:37:40,329 --> 02:37:43,059
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}这有一个大问题......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}and that is the great question...

1613
02:37:43,132 --> 02:37:45,999
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我写的好吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}will I ever be able to write well?

1614
02:37:46,068 --> 02:37:48,559
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我想要的太多了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I want to so much.

1615
02:37:48,637 --> 02:37:51,299
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我想要我死后还继续活着
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I want to go on living even after my death.

1616
02:38:17,266 --> 02:38:20,064
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}又响了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}There it goes again.

1617
02:38:20,135 --> 02:38:22,194
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}弗兰克先生。听到没有？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Frank, do you hear?

1618
02:38:22,271 --> 02:38:24,967
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}是的，听到了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Yes, I hear.

1619
02:38:25,040 --> 02:38:27,975
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}这是第三次了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}This is the third time.

1620
02:38:28,043 --> 02:38:32,309
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}连续第三次了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}The third time in quick succession.

1621
02:38:32,381 --> 02:38:35,043
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}是一个信号
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It's a signal.

1622
02:38:35,117 --> 02:38:37,881
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我说是米耶普要联系我们
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I tell you it's Miep trying to get us.

1623
02:38:39,054 --> 02:38:41,045
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}由于某种原因――她不能过来......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}For some reason she-- she can't come to us...

1624
02:38:41,123 --> 02:38:43,091
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}她在试图警告我们什么事
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}and she's trying to warn us of something.

1625
02:38:43,158 --> 02:38:45,149
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}请不要这样，达索尔先生。
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Please, Mr. Dussel. Please.

1626
02:38:45,227 --> 02:38:48,685
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你在白费口舌
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You're wasting your breath.

1627
02:38:48,764 --> 02:38:52,359
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}一定是发生什么事情了。弗兰克先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Something has happened, Mr. Frank.

1628
02:38:52,434 --> 02:38:56,837
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}米耶普已经三天没来看我们了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It's been three days now that Miep hasn't been to see us.

1629
02:39:03,345 --> 02:39:06,178
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}今天没有一个人来上班
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And today not a man has come to work.

1630
02:39:06,248 --> 02:39:08,614
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}楼里面鸦雀无声
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}There hasn't been a sound in the building.

1631
02:39:09,985 --> 02:39:12,010
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}或许是星期日
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Perhaps it's Sunday.

1632
02:39:12,087 --> 02:39:14,078
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们或许都没法判断日期了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We may have lost track of the days.

1633
02:39:15,224 --> 02:39:18,682
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你有这本日记。今天星期几？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You with the diary there, what day is it?

1634
02:39:18,760 --> 02:39:21,991
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我没忘记日期
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I don't lose track of the days.

1635
02:39:22,064 --> 02:39:24,225
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我知道今天星期几
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I know exactly what day it is.

1636
02:39:25,801 --> 02:39:29,100
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}是星期五，八月四日
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It's Friday, the fourth of August.

1637
02:39:29,171 --> 02:39:31,901
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}今天星期五，却没有一个人上班
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}It's Friday, and not a man at work.

1638
02:39:35,811 --> 02:39:38,075
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}告诉你，卡勒先生死了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I tell you, Mr. Kraler is dead.

1639
02:39:39,281 --> 02:39:41,306
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}那是唯一的解释
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}That's the only explanation.

1640
02:39:41,383 --> 02:39:43,613
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}他死了，这栋楼歇业了......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}He's dead, and they've closed down the building...

1641
02:39:43,685 --> 02:39:45,619
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}那就是米耶普试图告诉我们的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}and that's what Miep's trying to tell us.

1642
02:39:45,687 --> 02:39:48,087
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}可能她从来没给我们打过电话，达索尔先生
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}She would never telephone us, Mr. Dussel.

1643
02:39:48,156 --> 02:39:50,681
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我求你了，弗兰克先生，去接电话
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Please, I beg of you, Mr. Frank, answer the phone.

1644
02:39:50,759 --> 02:39:53,284
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-不  。-接起来就可以。你不必说话
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- No. -Just listen. You don't have to speak.

1645
02:39:53,362 --> 02:39:56,490
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}只是听听，看是不是米耶普
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Just listen and see if it's Miep.

1646
02:39:56,565 --> 02:39:59,193
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}看在上帝的份上，去接电话！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}For God's sake, answer the telephone!

1647
02:39:59,268 --> 02:40:01,293
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我说了，不
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I've told you, no.

1648
02:40:06,575 --> 02:40:10,534
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我不会做任何事情，让别人知道我们在这栋楼里
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I'll do nothing that might let anyone know that we're in this building.

1649
02:40:10,612 --> 02:40:13,137
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}弗兰克先生是正确的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Frank's right.

1650
02:40:13,215 --> 02:40:15,479
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不用告诉我们你赞成谁
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}There's no need to tell us what side you're on.

1651
02:40:15,551 --> 02:40:20,750
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}如果我们就这么安静，耐心地等着，我相信会有帮助到来的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}If we wait here quietly and patiently, I believe that help will come.

1652
02:40:27,796 --> 02:40:30,560
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}达索尔先生......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Mr. Dussel...

1653
02:40:30,632 --> 02:40:33,624
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不，达......达索尔先生......达索尔先生！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}No, Mr.... Mr. Dussel... Mr. Dussel!

1654
02:40:48,150 --> 02:40:50,084
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}太迟了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Too late.

1655
02:40:57,392 --> 02:41:01,920
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}就这么一直等着......等到死
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}So we just wait here... until we die.

1656
02:41:01,997 --> 02:41:04,795
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我受不了了。我要自杀
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I can't stand it. I'll kill myself.

1657
02:41:04,866 --> 02:41:07,460
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}看在老天的份上，别说话
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}For heaven's sake, stop it.

1658
02:41:07,536 --> 02:41:11,063
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}要是我自杀，你会高兴的。你愿意要我死
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I think you would be glad if I did. You want me to die.

1659
02:41:11,139 --> 02:41:13,130
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们在这里是谁的错？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Whose fault is it we're here?

1660
02:41:13,208 --> 02:41:15,836
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我们本来可以在美国或者瑞士很安全
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}We could have been safe in America or Switzerland.

1661
02:41:15,911 --> 02:41:19,039
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不，不。我想离开的时候，你却不愿意离开
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}But no, no. You wouldn't leave when I wanted to.

1662
02:41:19,114 --> 02:41:21,378
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你舍不得你那些值钱的东西
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You couldn't leave your precious things.

1663
02:41:21,450 --> 02:41:23,918
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-你的家具。  -是那样
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}- Your furniture. - That's right.

1664
02:41:23,986 --> 02:41:27,080
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}全都怪我。都是我的错
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Blame it all on me. It's all my fault.

1665
02:41:27,155 --> 02:41:29,783
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你的帽子，你的鞋，还有那些碟子
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Your hats,your shoes,your dishes.

1666
02:41:29,858 --> 02:41:32,122
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}不就是为了让你过的舒适才弄那些吗
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}For your comfort we had anything.

1667
02:41:32,194 --> 02:41:36,028
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-我的舒适。  -我从来没有过我想要的东西
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}-My comfort. - I never had anything I really wanted.

1668
02:41:36,098 --> 02:41:38,157
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}哪个不是为了让你高兴！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Everything was for your pleasure!

1669
02:41:45,240 --> 02:41:49,142
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}看，彼得。看天空
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Look, Peter. Look at the sky.

1670
02:41:50,445 --> 02:41:53,710
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}那些云彩漂亮吧？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Aren't the clouds beautiful?

1671
02:41:55,083 --> 02:41:57,881
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}好好可爱的一天
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}A lovely, lovely day.

1672
02:42:07,062 --> 02:42:08,996
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你知道我要做的吗......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You know what I do...

1673
02:42:09,064 --> 02:42:12,932
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}当我无法再忍受哪怕一分钟被关在笼子里的时候
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}when I think I can't stand another minute of being cooped up?

1674
02:42:14,936 --> 02:42:16,961
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我想象着我在外面了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I think myself outside.

1675
02:42:19,841 --> 02:42:23,607
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}我想象着我在公园里散步，那个我常和爸爸一起去的......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}I think I'm on a walk in the park where I used to go with father...

1676
02:42:23,679 --> 02:42:27,706
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}漫坡都是番红花，长寿花，还有紫罗兰的地方
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}where the crocus and the jonquils and the violets grow along the slopes.

1677
02:42:32,521 --> 02:42:35,490
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你知道......
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You know...

1678
02:42:35,557 --> 02:42:40,085
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你想过在外面最美好的是什么吗？
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}the most wonderful part of thinking yourself outside?

1679
02:42:47,335 --> 02:42:50,168
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你可以随心所欲做你想要做的
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You can have it any way you like.

1680
02:42:52,674 --> 02:42:57,304
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}你可以让玫瑰花，紫罗兰，郁金香都在一个季节里开放
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}You can have roses, violets and tulips all blooming in the same season.

1681
02:43:00,716 --> 02:43:03,048
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}多美妙啊！
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}Isn't that wonderful?

1682
02:43:07,355 --> 02:43:11,291
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}当我以前在外面的时候，我一直认为什么都理所当然
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}When I was outside, I used to take it all for granted.

1683
02:43:11,359 --> 02:43:14,487
{\fn黑体\fs12\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}现在在这里，一想到大自然，我都要疯了
{\fs9\bord1\shad0\pos(200,250)}And now in here I've just gone crazy about nature.

